strings: <voice_0x01001596><se_high>breathe!: Are you my bodyguard? Oh Grace, you are completely helpless!
<voice_0x01001597><se_high>breathe!: You cannot be fired before finding a job or before finishing your job. but i think i can! ??
<voice_0x01001598><se_high>breathe!: Such a beautiful insult! He agreed!
<voice_0x01001599><se_high>breathe!: the best brother! That's okay, I forgive you
<voice_0x0100159A><se_high>breathe!: Not bad, at least sorry for disappointing me
<voice_0x0100159B><se_high>breathe!: forgive me please but next time don't wait until things settle down. I'm trying that trick again and uploading my own, you know.
<voice_0x0100159C><se_def><IF_SOLO>rice: Ah, the Forgotten Guardian is back!<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>rice: The forgotten guardian is back!<ENDIF_SOLO>
<voice_0x0100159D><se_def>rice: The game can be played by 2 persons.
<voice_0x0100159E><se_def>rice: I decided to forget to mention the price! I bought it for you when I forgot about everything!
<voice_0x0100159F><se_def>rice: Outstanding! You really don't think you'll get half your money, do you?????
<voice_0x010015A0><se_def>rice: I chose to use it! have a good day! welcome
